translate portuguese lisalivingroom_acb88e92:

    # "Lisa's not here watching TV like she usually is. What's going on with her?"
    "A Lisa não está aqui a ver televisão como costuma estar. O que se passa com ela?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:4
translate portuguese lisalivingroom_b428ebd3:

    # "I guess she's still upset. Better just give her time."
    "Acho que ainda está chateada. É melhor dar-lhe tempo."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:16
translate portuguese lisalivingroom_28820f39:

    # "Lisa is in the living room watching television."
    "A Lisa está na sala a ver televisão."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:17
translate portuguese lisalivingroom_62054172:

    # sp "Hey, honey, I'm just watching some TV. Want to join me?"
    sp "Olá, querida, estou só a ver televisão. Queres juntar-te a mim?"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:21
translate portuguese lisatv_11b9ab1f:

    # sp "Sure, that sounds great."
    sp "Claro, parece-me ótimo."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:25
translate portuguese lisatv_683befdb:

    # "Lisa changes into her nightgown and we go sit in the living room together."
    "A Lisa veste a camisa de dormir e vamos sentar-nos juntos na sala de estar."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:115
translate portuguese lisatvconversation_8d017aa1:

    # "I sit down next to her and we watch television together for a while."
    "Sento-me ao lado dela e vemos televisão juntos por um bocado."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:117
translate portuguese lisatvconversation_3f78d36e:

    # "After the show is over, Lisa looks over to me."
    "Depois do programa acabar, a Lisa olha para mim."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:118
translate portuguese lisatvconversation_9938deea:

    # sp "Well, it's getting late. I'm going to go to bed, honey."
    sp "Bem, está a ficar tarde. Vou para a cama, querido."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:119
translate portuguese lisatvconversation_db98731b:

    # pc "Alright, [mom]."
    pc "Tudo bem, [mom]."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:120
translate portuguese lisatvconversation_b7fc26cb:

    # sp "Thanks for hanging out with me. Love you."
    sp "Obrigada por teres ficado comigo. Amo-te."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:121
translate portuguese lisatvconversation_776fd6b3:

    # pc "Love you too, [mom]. Good night."
    pc "Também te amo, [mom]. Boa noite."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:122
translate portuguese lisatvconversation_0ffd2107:

    # sp "Good night."
    sp "Boa noite."

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisalivingroom.rpy:123
translate portuguese lisatvconversation_b9d79178:

    # "She gets up and walks towards her bedroom. I don't really want to watch any more TV, so I turn it off and leave as well."
    "Ela levanta-se e caminha em direção ao quarto. Não tenho muita vontade de ver mais televisão, por isso desligo-a e saio também."

